{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she tried to get back some of our possessions-- at least so we can stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was unsuccessful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Still, she managed, somehow, we stayed for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all I remember, that she was managed to get me some food and shelter, of course, for the both of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took weeks and weeks until I was able to even function.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all I remembered, that I would wash myself, always, in the dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't look at myself, because as I can encircle my wrist, here, that's how I used to encircle my arm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was absolutely a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I looked like a seven-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, when I got better, she wanted to get out of there, as fast as possible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We never asked back to get our personal things, nor our possessions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only thing she was able to get from the mayor of the town, who certified that, indeed, we lived there, and my father owned a pharmacy, and with that, we left.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she made up her mind, where we want to be is in Rome, in Italy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Her son was there, and that was a safe place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's where we headed, a roundabout way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went, first, to Bratislava, which was the capital of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No sooner did we get there, I was back in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got jaundiced, and I was quite ill for weeks and weeks, in the hospital in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then when I got better, somehow-- it must have been the government-- sent us, which was very nice, to the [INAUDIBLE] mountains, to recuperate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the minute I got better, we started a journey to-- through Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How we got to Vienna, I do not know.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
